    "body": "An example of what pandas also does is making a legend by default:\n\n```\nIn [16]: %timeit df.plot()\n1 loops, best of 3: 3.45 s per loop\n\nIn [17]: %timeit df.plot(legend=False)\n1 loops, best of 3: 2.24 s per loop\n```\n\nSo that is already a big part of the difference in this case. \n"
